divs: Sighting DetailsIt looks like a very bright star, slightly larger than Jupitor moving slowly in a slight ziz zag motion. I have seen these things on several ocations some times they apear and disapear and apear again moving from one direction or another but this one went directly over DIA Airport from west to east, apearing aprox 20 degrees abouve the western horizon and disapearing at about 20 degrees above the eastern horizon.
